### 把 token 放在这里（不用加花括号）
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIyIiwidXNlcm5hbWUiOiJ0ZXN0MSIsInJvbGUiOiJVU0VSIiwiaWF0IjoxNzY2OTM3MDI2LCJleHAiOjE3NjcwMjM0MjZ9.oX_gaCQmLJU8rT704DfYB1G0qvEGsNSJIQlYjnF737w

### 1) 分类列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/learn/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2) 课程列表（不筛选）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/learn/courses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3) 课程列表（按分类筛选）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/learn/courses?categoryId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4) 课程详情（courseId 改成真实ID）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/learn/course/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5) 课程课时列表（courseId 改成真实ID）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/learn/course/1/lessons
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6) 课时详情（lessonId 改成真实ID）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/learn/lesson/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7) 上报进度（示例：学到 40%）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/learn/my/progress/upsert?courseId=1&lessonId=1&progressPercent=40&status=LEARNING
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8) 查询我在某课程的进度
GET http://localhost:8080/api/learn/my/progress/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9) 查询我的进度列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/learn/my/progress
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
